# Site memory

Before work in `site/`:

1. Read `site/.memory/hub.md`
2. Read `site/.memory/tasks/active.md`
3. Open the relevant card under `site/.memory/tasks/cards/`

Todos live in **active + cards** only. Do not update Obsidian `memory/tasks/kanban.md` for site tasks.

Do not load the full monorepo `memory/` tree. Platform ADR/history only when needed (single files under `memory/docs/adr/` or `memory/hub.md`).

After a meaningful step: update the card, `active.md` if WIP changed, and append `site/.memory/history.md`.
